      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m listing my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream! This car is in pristine, mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garage-parked, and it still has that brand-new feel. The paint is flawless and the interior is completely spotless. It drives like a charm and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is definitely the one. Come by and take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
