    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a concours-level example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features a perfectly indexed VANOS system and crisp individual throttle body response. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, featuring reinforced subframe mounting points and a factory-spec limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque vectoring. Every bushing is pliable, the suspension geometry remains true, and the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, mechanical throws with zero synchro drag. This is a turn-key collector piece with zero deferred maintenance and flawless factory paint depth.",
